n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔中失敗後我都唸左好多野，頹左一排，研究左好耐究竟我地抗爭有咩意義，齋行又無用，衝又會俾人拉又失民心，我地無權無勢，一日起中共政權下都唔會逆轉到⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n之後我唸通左，任何抗爭方法都其實係喚醒我地既憤怒，同埋將思想盛傳，我地仲後生，係都係依班當權者死先，到時就係趁有呢d動盪時期各方面就乘虛而入、乘勝追擊<br />\n<br />\n所以任何方法抗爭都好，都要留返條命，同留返個思想起度，唔好放棄，長命功夫長命做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac224c24d56bdd30ab39f850cea184958b3f175","tid":1248364,"uid":44916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"其他地方衝可以，警總衝會死"},{"pid":"a2fb8116d0ddccfa68eaa0c9884409b39cc3cb02","tid":1248364,"uid":197332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5015a42154e870236678255625d04bc30d569ee2","tid":1248364,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a191b61d8eeb503be562f93650a658b16b6600d","tid":1248364,"uid":197332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f62f3a5b758657cfc3c165f23b507b5c246a298","tid":1248364,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"不過你同時要知道g20之後冇得衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"係點都唔沖 g20前後都冇分別 總之就唔沖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"你知道就得<br />\n希望你堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"我已經出到腳板底甩哂皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係絕對要繼續和理非"},{"pid":"de84fdbd95d35d1f61740caf47b8a996fc45bd6f","tid":1248364,"uid":197332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aac224c24d56bdd30ab39f850cea184958b3f175","tid":1248364,"uid":44916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"其他地方衝可以，警總衝會死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"係 邊撚度都唔得 一個地方沖直接收全部地方皮<br />\n<br />\n唔好妖言惑眾ok？"},{"pid":"96a68e6b41d074476d0ca5522b074823b3bb2aae","tid":1248364,"uid":197332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":